Krissy Gear (born July 20, 1999) is an American professional middle distance runner and World Championship steeplechase from Fort Myers, Florida. At the 2023 Budapest World Championship, Gear represents Team USA.  Gear placed 10th at 2018 World U20 Championships. She is the 2023 USA Champion and 2018 USA U20 Champion.
